<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,356,1368,1395]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Lichenodraculus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Braun, H." box="[364,515,1368,1395]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" pagination="33 - 39" refId="ref38372" refString="Braun, H. (2011) The Little Lichen Dragon - an extraordinary katydid from the Ecuadorian Andes (Orthoptera, Tettigoniidae, Phaneropterinae, Dysoniini). Zootaxa, 3032 (1), 33 - 39. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3032.1.3" type="journal article" year="2011">Braun, 2011</bibRefCitation>
